                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-2240-18410823 t18410823-2240-punishment-262"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def3-2240-18410823 t18410823-2240-punishment-262"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against Ricketts and Skiggs.)</p>
